data.description: Nestled in San Francisco's coveted Outer Sunset, this home merges charm with proximity to all that the Sunset District has to offer. Sunlit living spaces feature an authentic fireplace, leading to a formal dining area. Two spacious bedrooms upstairs and a versatile third on the ground floor plus a bonus space perfect for an at home office for remote work. One full bathroom on each level. The gourmet kitchen invites culinary delight, while the curated garden provides a serene outdoor escape. A spacious tandem garage offers practicality with potential for growth. Moments from Noriega Street's amenities and the Sunset Recreational Center, urban conveniences meet coastal tranquility. Dive into Outer Sunset living at 1614 35th Avenue. Schedule your exclusive tour today.
